---
title: Pulled Pork Noodle Wok with stir-fried veg
description: The wok is a utensil that has, for centuries, been utilised in Chinese cuisine. Not quite the same as a frying pan, its bowl-like shape makes it especially suited to stir-frying, so if you've got one at home, use yours to make this tasty noodle dish.
